   English equivalents, example sentences) is included.

Transformation
--------------

The `scripts/` directory contains the exact pipeline used to produce the
merged SQLite. Running these scripts on the upstream sources (in the
versions referenced above) will reproduce `bookear-dict-v1.sqlite` byte
for byte.

  - scripts/build_oewn.py   — OEWN LMF XML → oewn.sqlite
  - scripts/build_krdict.py — KRDict XML → krdict.sqlite (English-keyed index)
  - scripts/merge.py        — merges both into bookear-dict-v1.sqlite

